<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>本地博客管理系统</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    header {
      background-color: #333;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    h1 {
      margin: 0;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #4CAF50;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .btn:hover {
      background-color: #45a049;
    }
    .features {
      margin-top: 40px;
    }
    .feature {
      background-color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .feature h3 {
      color: #333;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>本地博客管理系统</h1>
    <p>动态编辑，静态部署</p>
  </header>
  <div class="container">
    <a href="/admin" class="btn">进入管理后台</a>
    
    <div class="features">
      <div class="feature">
        <h3>动态管理</h3>
        <p>本地运行的动态网站，提供直观的后台管理界面，方便添加和修改博客。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <h3>静态部署</h3>
        <p>生成纯静态网站数据，可轻松部署到GitHub Pages等静态托管服务。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <h3>视频支持</h3>
        <p>支持嵌入优酷等外部视频平台的视频内容。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <h3>简单易用</h3>
        <p>无需复杂配置，一键生成和部署静态网站。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>